Schaeuble Seeks Euro Area Transaction Tax This Year, Bild Says

-- B y   N a o m i   K r e s g e
-- 
2011-09-17T09:22:02Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-17/schaeuble-seeks-euro-area-transaction-tax-this-year-bild-says.html
German Finance Minister  Wolfgang Schaeuble  said a financial transaction tax should be introduced
in the euro area this year,  Bild am Sonntag  reported today in a
preview of an interview to be published tomorrow.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Naomi Kresge in Berlin at 
